title: Pavel Tsvetkov's 'Desperate Love' Book of P
description:
Dear Friends,

the current upload contains several pages from the .html presentation of Pavel Tsvetkov&#039;s &#039;Desperate Love&#039; book of poems, which can be read in full at www.paveltsvetkov.com

The texts are written in Cyrillic and unless one knows Bulgarian, it is unlikely that he/she will be able to understand the meaning of the words.


The current torrent contains v2.1 of the upload files.
